text: Rajendra Laxmi Gaire is a politician in Nepal and a member of the Communist Party of Nepal, is known by his Nepali name of (Unified Marxist-Leninist). She was chosen in the Nepalese National Assembly election of 2022 and is also a member of the Rashtriya Sabha. ==References== ==Other websites== *सदस्यहरु Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Nepalese politicians
